00:38:49.710 --> 00:38:54.210 align:middle line:84%
and then had this
nonverbal voice.

00:38:54.210 --> 00:38:58.860 align:middle line:84%
It wasn't in English, but it
was this kind of voice in me

00:38:58.860 --> 00:39:02.770 align:middle line:84%
that said that I had this
really amazing, strong purpose

00:39:02.770 --> 00:39:05.170 align:middle line:90%
and it wasn't my time to leave.

00:39:05.170 --> 00:39:09.000 align:middle line:84%
And as this was being
said, I could kind of

00:39:09.000 --> 00:39:10.630 align:middle line:90%
see that I was being revived.

00:39:10.630 --> 00:39:13.840 align:middle line:84%
And then I just literally
shot back into my body.

00:39:13.840 --> 00:39:15.420 align:middle line:84%
And it was a really
awful feeling,

00:39:15.420 --> 00:39:22.020 align:middle line:84%
because you have this amazing,
unworldly, peaceful feeling

00:39:22.020 --> 00:39:23.490 align:middle line:90%
as soon as you leave your body.

00:39:23.490 --> 00:39:25.950 align:middle line:84%
And then you shoot back into
it, and it was right back

00:39:25.950 --> 00:39:30.210 align:middle line:84%
into this excruciating,
horrible pain and confusion,

00:39:30.210 --> 00:39:32.880 align:middle line:84%
and not knowing where I
was, or what happened,

00:39:32.880 --> 00:39:36.180 align:middle line:84%
and just knowing that I was
blind, and could hardly hear,

00:39:36.180 --> 00:39:38.820 align:middle line:84%
and had people screaming
and crying around me,

00:39:38.820 --> 00:39:42.010 align:middle line:90%
and people banging on my chest.

00:39:42.010 --> 00:39:46.110 align:middle line:84%
And it wasn't the greatest
feeling in the world.

00:39:46.110 --> 00:39:49.160 align:middle line:90%


00:39:49.160 --> 00:39:51.660 align:middle line:10%
>> In one dramatic
blind-from-birth individual

00:39:51.660 --> 00:39:54.420 align:middle line:10%
that I interviewed--
her name was Vicki--

00:39:54.420 --> 00:39:55.960 align:middle line:10%
she had a severe auto accident.

00:39:55.960 --> 00:40:00.000 align:middle line:10%
