and she was clinically dying.

00:40:00.000 --> 00:40:02.040 align:middle line:10%
And her consciousness
separated from the body.

00:40:02.040 --> 00:40:04.740 align:middle line:10%
And all of a sudden
her point of reference

00:40:04.740 --> 00:40:06.420 align:middle line:10%
was up on the roof,
near the roof,

00:40:06.420 --> 00:40:08.220 align:middle line:10%
near the ceiling of
the emergency room.

00:40:08.220 --> 00:40:10.980 align:middle line:84%
And she looked down and
saw a being laid out

00:40:10.980 --> 00:40:13.180 align:middle line:90%
on an emergency room bed.

00:40:13.180 --> 00:40:14.069 align:middle line:90%
She was terrified.

00:40:14.069 --> 00:40:16.110 align:middle line:84%
This was the first visual
experience of her life,

00:40:16.110 --> 00:40:18.120 align:middle line:84%
and she didn't know
what to do with it.

00:40:18.120 --> 00:40:20.940 align:middle line:84%
She didn't even know that
that was her body until all

00:40:20.940 --> 00:40:23.670 align:middle line:84%
of a sudden she correlated
what she had been able to feel

00:40:23.670 --> 00:40:25.590 align:middle line:90%
in her life-- her long hair--

00:40:25.590 --> 00:40:28.110 align:middle line:84%
and she felt a ring, of
course, when she was blind.

00:40:28.110 --> 00:40:29.640 align:middle line:90%
But now she could see it.

00:40:29.640 --> 00:40:31.140 align:middle line:90%
And she was able to correlate.

00:40:31.140 --> 00:40:34.200 align:middle line:84%
Only through correlating what
she'd previously known only

00:40:34.200 --> 00:40:37.260 align:middle line:84%
through a sense of touch
with her sudden new visual

00:40:37.260 --> 00:40:40.920 align:middle line:84%
impressions, she realized,
gosh, that's what I look like.

00:40:40.920 --> 00:40:42.990 align:middle line:84%
And it was an
incredible revelation.

00:40:42.990 --> 00:40:45.090 align:middle line:84%
Beginning of a
very, very detailed

00:40:45.090 --> 00:40:46.620 align:middle line:90%
visual near-death experience.

00:40:46.620 --> 00:40:53.480 align:middle line:90%


00:40:53.480 --> 00:40:57.290 align:middle line:84%
>> If we want to know the
absolute truth about how

00:40:57.290 --> 00:41:01.220 align:middle line:84%
to experience enlightenment,
we can seek spiritual advice

00:41:01.220 --> 00:41:04.830 align:middle line:84%
and leadership from those who
have attained enlightenment.

00:41:04.830 --> 00:41:07.550 align:middle line:84%
But if we can't have access
to enlightened teachers

00:41:07.550 --> 00:41:11.690 align:middle line:84%
in the body, in the flesh,
one of the ways to do this

00:41:11.690 --> 00:41:14.930 align:middle line:84%
is to ask for guidance
from our dreams, visions,

00:41:14.930 --> 00:41:17.510 align:middle line:84%
and even to receive
our own apparitions

00:41:17.510 --> 00:41:20.330 align:middle line:90%
of the ascended masters.

00:41:20.330 --> 00:41:23.460 align:middle line:84%
There are three ways
that visions can occur.

00:41:23.460 --> 00:41:25.940 align:middle line:84%
One is through direct
face-to-face apparitions

00:41:25.940 --> 00:41:28.610 align:middle line:84%
or appearances of
enlightened ones.

00:41:28.610 --> 00:41:31.450 align:middle line:84%
These appearances can
sometimes be private,

00:41:31.450 --> 00:41:33.980 align:middle line:84%
where a neighboring
person to the visionary

00:41:33.980 --> 00:41:37.250 align:middle line:84%
would not be able to
see the apparition.

00:41:37.250 --> 00:41:40.670 align:middle line:84%
Second is through
dreams, and third is

00:41:40.670 --> 00:41:44.180 align:middle line:90%
during near-death experiences.

00:41:44.180 --> 00:41:46.520 align:middle line:84%
>> Religious figures have
been described in near-death

00:41:46.520 --> 00:41:49.470 align:middle line:84%
experiences over
and over and over.

00:41:49.470 --> 00:41:51.140 align:middle line:10%
We have a relatively
small number

00:41:51.140 --> 00:41:54.390 align:middle line:10%
