although we have seen that.

00:42:00.800 --> 00:42:03.440 align:middle line:84%
The overwhelming majority of
experiences shared with us

00:42:03.440 --> 00:42:05.930 align:middle line:84%
on the website are, of
course, from people that

00:42:05.930 --> 00:42:07.640 align:middle line:90%
had a Christian background.

00:42:07.640 --> 00:42:12.060 align:middle line:84%
Jesus appears in about 5% to
10% of near-death experiences.

00:42:12.060 --> 00:42:13.760 align:middle line:84%
And again, strikingly,
there seems

00:42:13.760 --> 00:42:17.660 align:middle line:84%
to be some amazing consistency
in how Jesus is described.

00:42:17.660 --> 00:42:21.525 align:middle line:84%
If Jesus is with other people
in a near-death experience,

00:42:21.525 --> 00:42:23.900 align:middle line:84%
the great majority of the time
the near-death experiencer

00:42:23.900 --> 00:42:28.160 align:middle line:84%
will feel an intensely loving
presence in this Jesus.

00:42:28.160 --> 00:42:30.360 align:middle line:84%
Far, far more than
the other people.

00:42:30.360 --> 00:42:32.570 align:middle line:84%
He may have more
light about him.

00:42:32.570 --> 00:42:35.310 align:middle line:84%
Often, when they interact with
Jesus, it's really interesting,

00:42:35.310 --> 00:42:37.010 align:middle line:84%
because a lot of us
would have thought,

00:42:37.010 --> 00:42:39.650 align:middle line:84%
well, Jesus would
preach and sort of

00:42:39.650 --> 00:42:42.050 align:middle line:84%
do you would expect to
do Jesus from the Bible.

00:42:42.050 --> 00:42:46.190 align:middle line:84%
But in near-death experiences
Jesus' top priority seems

00:42:46.190 --> 00:42:49.760 align:middle line:84%
to be to listen, seems to be
sharing love and compassion,

00:42:49.760 --> 00:42:52.400 align:middle line:84%
seems to be to share
an overwhelming sense

00:42:52.400 --> 00:42:54.800 align:middle line:84%
of acceptance with the
individual that they're with.

00:42:54.800 --> 00:43:13.500 align:middle line:90%


00:43:13.500 --> 00:43:18.450 align:middle line:84%
>> In The Apocryphon of John, it
is written that 550 days after

00:43:18.450 --> 00:43:22.590 align:middle line:84%
