01:14:15.640 --> 01:14:17.740 align:middle line:90%
of their spheres.

01:14:17.740 --> 01:14:20.050 align:middle line:84%
And the light were their
thoughts, just like right now.

01:14:20.050 --> 01:14:22.150 align:middle line:84%
If I think an
apple or an orange,

01:14:22.150 --> 01:14:24.460 align:middle line:84%
I'm seeing it on the
screen of my mind.

01:14:24.460 --> 01:14:26.380 align:middle line:90%
I could see them thinking.

01:14:26.380 --> 01:14:28.720 align:middle line:84%
And also, I could
see that the vortex

01:14:28.720 --> 01:14:30.790 align:middle line:84%
of the knowledge
of good and evil

01:14:30.790 --> 01:14:35.290 align:middle line:84%
was creating the force field
of the cocoon around them.

01:14:35.290 --> 01:14:36.450 align:middle line:90%
And they weren't free.

01:14:36.450 --> 01:14:40.300 align:middle line:84%
And above them was this
supernatural light.

01:14:40.300 --> 01:14:43.347 align:middle line:84%
And I came over to some of
them, and I wanted to free them.

01:14:43.347 --> 01:14:44.930 align:middle line:84%
I wanted to say,
hey, wake up, there's

01:14:44.930 --> 01:14:47.260 align:middle line:84%
light on the other side
of this if you just

01:14:47.260 --> 01:14:50.020 align:middle line:84%
crack the egg open,
if you can get

01:14:50.020 --> 01:14:52.570 align:middle line:90%
past the fear and the shaking.

01:14:52.570 --> 01:14:54.070 align:middle line:90%
And none of them could do it.

01:14:54.070 --> 01:14:56.800 align:middle line:84%
The angel told me that
there's nothing I could do.

01:14:56.800 --> 01:14:58.540 align:middle line:90%
None of them were ready yet.

01:14:58.540 --> 01:15:00.340 align:middle line:84%
And all of a
sudden, I just left.

01:15:00.340 --> 01:15:02.320 align:middle line:84%
I left Earth, and
I started zooming

01:15:02.320 --> 01:15:05.250 align:middle line:84%
what appeared to be through
space and the galaxy.

01:15:05.250 --> 01:15:08.380 align:middle line:84%
And I looked down at my body
and it was completely human.

01:15:08.380 --> 01:15:12.430 align:middle line:84%
But it was so ultra-human
that if I used my hand

01:15:12.430 --> 01:15:15.730 align:middle line:84%
and closed my eye, I
could see like a telescope

01:15:15.730 --> 01:15:16.970 align:middle line:90%
through my fingertips.

01:15:16.970 --> 01:15:20.920 align:middle line:84%
I could see and hear
the music of the angels

01:15:20.920 --> 01:15:22.990 align:middle line:90%
through every pore of my being.

01:15:22.990 --> 01:15:25.160 align:middle line:84%
Eyesight was not
limited to the eyes.

01:15:25.160 --> 01:15:26.870 align:middle line:84%
It was happening
from everywhere.

01:15:26.870 --> 01:15:29.320 align:middle line:84%
I could see behind me,
underneath me, above me,

01:15:29.320 --> 01:15:30.350 align:middle line:90%
everywhere.

01:15:30.350 --> 01:15:34.340 align:middle line:84%
And I was zooming at
superluminal speeds,

01:15:34.340 --> 01:15:36.530 align:middle line:84%
thousands of times faster
than the speed of light

01:15:36.530 --> 01:15:38.120 align:middle line:90%
through the galaxy.

01:15:38.120 --> 01:15:41.450 align:middle line:84%
And as I was moving through
this first celestial heaven

01:15:41.450 --> 01:15:44.510 align:middle line:84%
of clear light
enlightenment, the light

01:15:44.510 --> 01:15:46.550 align:middle line:84%
itself told me that
there were millions

01:15:46.550 --> 01:15:49.352 align:middle line:84%
of paradise planets suspended
in this field of light.

01:15:49.352 --> 01:15:51.345 align:middle line:84%
But I didn't stop
on any of them.

01:15:51.345 --> 01:15:54.020 align:middle line:84%
And I got to the point where
I came to this membrane.

01:15:54.020 --> 01:15:56.000 align:middle line:90%
You could actually see it.

01:15:56.000 --> 01:15:58.940 align:middle line:84%
And the closer I got to it,
the ecstasy and the love

01:15:58.940 --> 01:16:00.750 align:middle line:90%
was crushing me.

01:16:00.750 --> 01:16:02.270 align:middle line:90%
It was so overwhelming.

01:16:02.270 --> 01:16:05.180 align:middle line:84%
It was more than I ever
dreamed enlightenment

01:16:05.180 --> 01:16:06.980 align:middle line:90%
to be its very self.

01:16:06.980 --> 01:16:09.490 align:middle line:84%
I mean, all these
years and meditation,

01:16:09.490 --> 01:16:12.680 align:middle line:84%
and this was way more ecstasy
and love than I ever, ever

01:16:12.680 --> 01:16:17.810 align:middle line:84%
dreamed how grand this
realization could be.

01:16:17.810 --> 01:16:19.520 align:middle line:84%
And as I approached
the membrane,

01:16:19.520 --> 01:16:23.710 align:middle line:84%
I became so crushed with
ecstasy it was unbearable.

01:16:23.710 --> 01:16:24.970 align:middle line:90%
Imagine too much love.

01:16:24.970 --> 01:16:27.470 align:middle line:84%
It's so much love that
you can't bear it.

01:16:27.470 --> 01:16:30.620 align:middle line:84%
And I went through the membrane
into the second clear light

01:16:30.620 --> 01:16:31.500 align:middle line:90%
heaven.

01:16:31.500 --> 01:16:34.700 align:middle line:84%
In the second clear light
heaven, everything, the love,

01:16:34.700 --> 01:16:36.600 align:middle line:84%
the ecstasy, the
peace, the power,

01:16:36.600 --> 01:16:39.620 align:middle line:84%
the beauty multiplied
another million times.

01:16:39.620 --> 01:16:41.270 align:middle line:90%
So it's exponential.

01:16:41.270 --> 01:16:44.330 align:middle line:84%
But miraculously, the
new body that I possessed

01:16:44.330 --> 01:16:46.610 align:middle line:84%
in the second heaven
of clear light

01:16:46.610 --> 01:16:50.150 align:middle line:84%
was able to sustain it
without being crushed.

01:16:50.150 --> 01:16:54.090 align:middle line:84%
And there I was, and my
field was at least 30 feet

01:16:54.090 --> 01:16:54.890 align:middle line:90%
beyond my body.

01:16:54.890 --> 01:16:56.420 align:middle line:90%
I still had arms and legs.

01:16:56.420 --> 01:17:00.170 align:middle line:84%
And I was zooming through the
universe at superluminal speed.

01:17:00.170 --> 01:17:03.140 align:middle line:84%
And the angels' singing
was louder, more beautiful.

01:17:03.140 --> 01:17:04.940 align:middle line:90%
I can hear it more clearly.

01:17:04.940 --> 01:17:06.830 align:middle line:84%
You could see
vortexes coming out

01:17:06.830 --> 01:17:09.320 align:middle line:84%
of the voices of
the angels, causing

01:17:09.320 --> 01:17:12.140 align:middle line:84%
the planets and the stars
and the solar systems

01:17:12.140 --> 01:17:14.230 align:middle line:90%
and the galaxies to be spinning.

01:17:14.230 --> 01:17:17.600 align:middle line:84%
And the subatomic particles,
you could see all of it

01:17:17.600 --> 01:17:19.850 align:middle line:84%
was caused by the
voices of angels.

01:17:19.850 --> 01:17:23.930 align:middle line:84%
They weren't just singing for
the beauty of God's choir.

01:17:23.930 --> 01:17:27.710 align:middle line:84%
They were singing to create
and sustain the creation.

01:17:27.710 --> 01:17:32.180 align:middle line:84%
It was very clear in this
omniscient knowledge.

01:17:32.180 --> 01:17:34.430 align:middle line:84%
And then I again
came to a membrane,

01:17:34.430 --> 01:17:38.030 align:middle line:84%
and the ecstasy started
crushing me torrentially.

01:17:38.030 --> 01:17:41.510 align:middle line:84%
And I went through the second
membrane into the third heaven.

01:17:41.510 --> 01:17:43.190 align:middle line:84%
And in the third
heaven, it multiplies

01:17:43.190 --> 01:17:45.690 align:middle line:90%
another million times.

01:17:45.690 --> 01:17:48.050 align:middle line:84%
It's billions of
times greater than I

01:17:48.050 --> 01:17:51.600 align:middle line:84%
thought enlightenment itself
would ever be at this point.

01:17:51.600 --> 01:17:55.280 align:middle line:84%
I mean, it's inconceivable
to the human brain

01:17:55.280 --> 01:17:57.890 align:middle line:84%
how much ecstasy God
has in store for us.

01:17:57.890 --> 01:18:00.740 align:middle line:84%
I mean, it just felt like
this is our birthright.

01:18:00.740 --> 01:18:03.180 align:middle line:90%
We all deserve this.

01:18:03.180 --> 01:18:07.190 align:middle line:84%
And my body was at least
100 feet wide in the light,

01:18:07.190 --> 01:18:10.580 align:middle line:84%
but I still had arms
and legs and hands.

01:18:10.580 --> 01:18:13.490 align:middle line:90%
I was a divine human form.

01:18:13.490 --> 01:18:16.790 align:middle line:84%
But I mean, not
even a millimeter

01:18:16.790 --> 01:18:17.850 align:middle line:90%
of suffering anywhere.

01:18:17.850 --> 01:18:20.290 align:middle line:84%
I mean, at this point,
I started to doubt

01:18:20.290 --> 01:18:22.430 align:middle line:84%
all enlightened masters
on Earth because I

01:18:22.430 --> 01:18:24.980 align:middle line:84%
didn't think that
anybody could function

01:18:24.980 --> 01:18:28.400 align:middle line:84%
in this much supreme love
and ecstasy and peace.

01:18:28.400 --> 01:18:31.430 align:middle line:84%
And the cosmic mind,
the sphere of my aura

01:18:31.430 --> 01:18:35.120 align:middle line:84%
was merging into the entire
universe, the galaxy.

01:18:35.120 --> 01:18:39.630 align:middle line:84%
It was just so
heavy and massive.

01:18:39.630 --> 01:18:42.350 align:middle line:90%
Who can walk around like this?

01:18:42.350 --> 01:18:45.650 align:middle line:84%
And then I came to the membrane
between the third and fourth.

01:18:45.650 --> 01:18:47.360 align:middle line:90%
And again, I was crushed.

01:18:47.360 --> 01:18:51.110 align:middle line:84%
It was unbearable, all of the
qualities of God in the light.

01:18:51.110 --> 01:18:52.980 align:middle line:90%
And I went into the fourth.

01:18:52.980 --> 01:18:55.310 align:middle line:84%
And the fourth, to me,
it was the beginning

01:18:55.310 --> 01:18:56.780 align:middle line:90%
of the unspeakable.

01:18:56.780 --> 01:18:58.130 align:middle line:90%
I had no arms and legs.

01:18:58.130 --> 01:18:59.180 align:middle line:90%
No body.

01:18:59.180 --> 01:19:02.990 align:middle line:84%
I became a field of light that
was many, many light years

01:19:02.990 --> 01:19:03.790 align:middle line:90%
across.

01:19:03.790 --> 01:19:05.930 align:middle line:90%
I mean, enormous in size.

01:19:05.930 --> 01:19:11.180 align:middle line:84%
My body that I was was
light years across.

01:19:11.180 --> 01:19:13.910 align:middle line:84%
And then, as I approached
the edge of the fourth

01:19:13.910 --> 01:19:19.160 align:middle line:84%
into the fifth, the exponential
increases in God's glory,

01:19:19.160 --> 01:19:21.080 align:middle line:90%
they become unspeakable.

01:19:21.080 --> 01:19:24.320 align:middle line:84%
It is unimaginable to a
human mind what is going

01:19:24.320 --> 01:19:26.550 align:middle line:90%
on inside of these fields.

01:19:26.550 --> 01:19:28.890 align:middle line:84%
The fields themselves
are conscious.

01:19:28.890 --> 01:19:30.020 align:middle line:90%
They are alive.

01:19:30.020 --> 01:19:32.000 align:middle line:90%
They always existed.

01:19:32.000 --> 01:19:36.050 align:middle line:84%
It's not that I egotistically
became as big as the field

01:19:36.050 --> 01:19:37.940 align:middle line:90%
as if I projected out.

01:19:37.940 --> 01:19:39.750 align:middle line:84%
These fields have
always existed.

01:19:39.750 --> 01:19:43.370 align:middle line:84%
And when we become one with
these rings, these spheres

01:19:43.370 --> 01:19:47.360 align:middle line:84%
of consciousness, we get access
to everything the field knows,

01:19:47.360 --> 01:19:49.331 align:middle line:90%
which is universal.

01:19:49.331 --> 01:19:51.080 align:middle line:84%
If you were Einstein,
you could understand

01:19:51.080 --> 01:19:55.210 align:middle line:84%
the physics and the vortices and
the vast knowledge of creation.

01:19:55.210 --> 01:19:58.670 align:middle line:84%
If you were da Vinci, you
could understand painting

01:19:58.670 --> 01:20:00.090 align:middle line:90%
beyond all dimensions.

01:20:00.090 --> 01:20:03.280 align:middle line:84%
And if you were Beethoven,
the music of the spheres,

01:20:03.280 --> 01:20:06.560 align:middle line:84%
if you could write it down, if
I could have written that down,

01:20:06.560 --> 01:20:08.720 align:middle line:84%
I would have created
symphonies beyond symphonies

01:20:08.720 --> 01:20:10.460 align:middle line:90%
for what I heard.

01:20:10.460 --> 01:20:14.820 align:middle line:90%
And then I went into the fifth.

01:20:14.820 --> 01:20:17.220 align:middle line:84%
And when I got to the
edge of the fifth,

01:20:17.220 --> 01:20:18.900 align:middle line:90%
I went into the sixth.

01:20:18.900 --> 01:20:22.920 align:middle line:84%
It is simply unimaginable what
is happening in the sixth.

01:20:22.920 --> 01:20:25.230 align:middle line:90%
It is inconceivable.

01:20:25.230 --> 01:20:27.660 align:middle line:90%
There is no sense of self.

01:20:27.660 --> 01:20:30.120 align:middle line:84%
It seems to be
completely extinguished.

01:20:30.120 --> 01:20:31.860 align:middle line:90%
There is no more David.

01:20:31.860 --> 01:20:35.970 align:middle line:84%
David the little man disappeared
into the Big Sky and was gone.

01:20:35.970 --> 01:20:37.750 align:middle line:84%
There was no trace
of him anymore.

01:20:37.750 --> 01:20:39.450 align:middle line:90%
It was just God.

01:20:39.450 --> 01:20:42.900 align:middle line:90%
The entire universe was my body.

01:20:42.900 --> 01:20:46.020 align:middle line:84%
And when I approached
the edge of the seventh,

01:20:46.020 --> 01:20:47.910 align:middle line:84%
the edge of the
seventh came and I

01:20:47.910 --> 01:20:51.250 align:middle line:84%
knew that if I
crossed that point,

01:20:51.250 --> 01:20:54.300 align:middle line:84%
something was going to
happen that was so massive,

01:20:54.300 --> 01:20:58.680 align:middle line:84%
so beyond my
abilities, that I felt

01:20:58.680 --> 01:21:01.920 align:middle line:84%
that my physical body would
terminate on the ground below,

01:21:01.920 --> 01:21:03.600 align:middle line:84%
and I wouldn't be
able to come back

01:21:03.600 --> 01:21:06.960 align:middle line:84%
to tell people that the
Kingdom of Heaven is real.

01:21:06.960 --> 01:21:10.200 align:middle line:84%
The desire to come
back was stronger

01:21:10.200 --> 01:21:12.094 align:middle line:84%
than the desire to
cross to find out

01:21:12.094 --> 01:21:13.260 align:middle line:90%
what was beyond the seventh.

01:21:13.260 --> 01:21:27.440 align:middle line:90%


01:21:27.440 --> 01:21:30.670 align:middle line:84%
>> In the "Lankavatara Sutra,"
it is written that Buddha

01:21:30.670 --> 01:21:35.620 align:middle line:84%
attained up to the sixth
samadhi over 400 lifetimes.

01:21:35.620 --> 01:21:38.410 align:middle line:84%
Buddha said that all the
samadhis up to the sixth

01:21:38.410 --> 01:21:40.180 align:middle line:90%
are impermanent.

01:21:40.180 --> 01:21:43.820 align:middle line:84%
Many attain some of them
thinking they are in nirvana

01:21:43.820 --> 01:21:46.210 align:middle line:90%
but remain deluded.

01:21:46.210 --> 01:21:49.900 align:middle line:84%
The nirvana of the
Tathagatas, full Buddhas,

01:21:49.900 --> 01:21:52.270 align:middle line:90%
begins at the seventh.

01:21:52.270 --> 01:21:56.530 align:middle line:84%
Nirvana for the Bodhisattva
is beyond the sixth,

01:21:56.530 --> 01:22:00.370 align:middle line:84%
into the seventh,
and beyond the ninth.

01:22:00.370 --> 01:22:02.980 align:middle line:84%
In order to go
beyond the sixth, one

01:22:02.980 --> 01:22:07.390 align:middle line:84%
has to come out of the
extreme ecstasy of this state

01:22:07.390 --> 01:22:11.260 align:middle line:84%
and do something
to uplift humanity.

01:22:11.260 --> 01:22:13.570 align:middle line:84%
Then, one can gain
the grace they

01:22:13.570 --> 01:22:17.230 align:middle line:84%
need to enter the
seventh and beyond.

01:22:17.230 --> 01:22:20.390 align:middle line:84%
>> There are the seven levels
of samadhi in the "Lankavatara

01:22:20.390 --> 01:22:24.460 align:middle line:84%
Sutra," but he mentions the
self-absorbed bliss states

01:22:24.460 --> 01:22:27.700 align:middle line:84%
where you can get trapped in
these bliss clouds and luminous

01:22:27.700 --> 01:22:29.650 align:middle line:90%
spheres for millions of years.

01:22:29.650 --> 01:22:30.580 align:middle line:90%
And it's not nirvana.

01:22:30.580 --> 01:22:31.800 align:middle line:90%
You're still in a more--

01:22:31.800 --> 01:22:34.270 align:middle line:84%
>> It's still a limited,
self-centered bliss.

01:22:34.270 --> 01:22:39.040 align:middle line:84%
It's not the what's called the
bliss void indivisible or bliss

01:22:39.040 --> 01:22:40.540 align:middle line:90%
freedom indivisible.

01:22:40.540 --> 01:22:42.860 align:middle line:84%
It's not the inconceivable,
ultimate bliss.

01:22:42.860 --> 01:22:49.270 align:middle line:90%


01:22:49.270 --> 01:22:54.430 align:middle line:84%
>> And fourth is three known
spheres or rings of nirvana,

01:22:54.430 --> 01:22:56.050 align:middle line:90%
God realization.

01:22:56.050 --> 01:22:58.570 align:middle line:84%
These stages are
documented and most common

01:22:58.570 --> 01:23:01.180 align:middle line:84%
to most of the major
world religions,

01:23:01.180 --> 01:23:05.831 align:middle line:84%
although they are expressed in
different languages or symbols.

01:23:05.831 --> 01:23:09.890 align:middle line:10%
>> Do the highest jnanas make--

01:23:09.890 --> 01:23:12.112 align:middle line:10%
are they so
transcendent of the body

01:23:12.112 --> 01:23:13.576 align:middle line:10%
that I wouldn't
even feel something

01:23:13.576 --> 01:23:15.040 align:middle line:10%
going through my foot?

01:23:15.040 --> 01:23:15.840 align:middle line:10%
>> Yeah.

01:23:15.840 --> 01:23:20.300 align:middle line:10%
Actually, I don't know
in our daily life,

01:23:20.300 --> 01:23:27.242 align:middle line:10%
but certainly in meditation we
can go beyond the sensation.

01:23:27.242 --> 01:23:31.194 align:middle line:84%
>> Beyond even a
painful sensation?

01:23:31.194 --> 01:23:33.700 align:middle line:90%
>> That is higher jnana.

01:23:33.700 --> 01:23:34.500 align:middle line:90%
>> Higher jnana.

01:23:34.500 --> 01:23:35.300 align:middle line:90%
>> Hm.

01:23:35.300 --> 01:23:37.520 align:middle line:90%
>> That's what I have heard.

01:23:37.520 --> 01:23:41.960 align:middle line:84%
>> If you go higher,
you don't feel nothing.

01:23:41.960 --> 01:23:44.593 align:middle line:84%
>> So if Jesus had
the nails in his body,

01:23:44.593 --> 01:23:48.500 align:middle line:84%
he didn't feel anything if
he was in the highest jnana?

01:23:48.500 --> 01:23:51.840 align:middle line:84%
>> But even further
in the Acts of John,

01:23:51.840 --> 01:23:56.460 align:middle line:84%
banned by Pope Leo the Great,
is yet another mystery.

01:23:56.460 --> 01:24:00.590 align:middle line:84%
During his own
crucifixion, Jesus Christ

01:24:00.590 --> 01:24:05.500 align:middle line:84%
reveals something that is an
utter iconoclasm to the church

01:24:05.500 --> 01:24:08.100 align:middle line:84%
and is further evidence as
to why Pope Leo the Great

01:24:08.100 --> 01:24:12.120 align:middle line:84%
ordered the gospel to be
burned and banned for all time.

01:24:12.120 --> 01:24:14.940 align:middle line:84%
Upon Jesus's arrest
in this gospel,

01:24:14.940 --> 01:24:19.190 align:middle line:84%
Jesus is dancing madly in a
circle with his disciples,

01:24:19.190 --> 01:24:21.270 align:middle line:84%
and his disciples are
all spinning around him,

01:24:21.270 --> 01:24:22.740 align:middle line:90%
and he's in the center.

01:24:22.740 --> 01:24:25.380 align:middle line:84%
And he's telling them to
dance and to celebrate

01:24:25.380 --> 01:24:29.790 align:middle line:84%
the moment of death and not to
fear death and fear the flesh,

01:24:29.790 --> 01:24:30.840 align:middle line:90%
but to celebrate.

01:24:30.840 --> 01:24:33.450 align:middle line:84%
And it's not Jesus
who is doubting

01:24:33.450 --> 01:24:36.030 align:middle line:84%
at the moment of his
arrest in the Acts of John,

01:24:36.030 --> 01:24:37.500 align:middle line:84%
it's the disciples
who are gloomy.

01:24:37.500 --> 01:24:39.120 align:middle line:90%
They don't want to dance.

01:24:39.120 --> 01:24:42.020 align:middle line:84%
They are terrified for
the loss of their master.

